            <h2>Try to pick the flexible travel deals</h2>
            <p>Flexible travel deals are those deals which are available during the off-season time and now you are looking to buy the airline tickets for the reservations because you need to manage the holiday booking on the flexible travel dates. You can search for the flights for the whole month or the whole quarter or the whole year to know, which month or which date is best for your travel. </p>
